Hey guy, I recently made a YouTube Let's Play channel (of which Kerbal Space Program Features) & I thought I'd use this opertunity to maybe see if any of you guys would like to Subscribe and/or give Feedback on my channel.

So my Name is Luke (A.K.A Pvt.Luek) I'm a 21 year male from England. As I already said I've recently made a Let's play channel (Its just short of 2 months Old) The Channels main focus is basically ANYTHING INDIE developed, as I generally find they're brilliant games of which the developer is actually nice enough to communicate with me (I've had a couple of developers from games I'm playing tweet videos & Subscribe to me which is a massive boost)

Check me out - http://www.youtube.com/user/PvtLuek

Anyway I'd apperciate if you guys would check out my channel, if you enjoy the videos please Subscribe as it means a lot to me. I'm also open to feedback if you guys want to post it below
